title: Sky Pirates Dakota Harris (1986 Australia) Indiana Jones rip-off
description:
Sky Pirates (1986 - Australia)                aka Dakota Harris

Adventure / Science Fiction

starring . . . . John Hargreaves, Meredith Phillips, Max Phipps
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0091964/


Filmed at Australia   |   Bora Bora, French Polynesia   |   Easter Island, Chile

World War II is about to come to an end. Meanwhile, the Australian military has come across a certain ancient device which can be used to travel in time. It is imperative that the Allies have it and that the Axis powers don't. The experienced aviator Lt. Harris gets assigned to transport the precious item to Washington, DC.

Yes, it's everything you want from an Indiana Jones rip-off. World War II . . . ancient astronauts . . . lost civilizations . . . the eerie heads of Easter Island . . . the powers of alien antimatter . . . daring aerial action . . . two-fisted wise cracking hero . . . and a pretty female sidekick. Yep. This sounds about right. So what the heck are we waiting for? Adventure awaits!!


Format: Matroska
Video : XviD, 720x304, 25.000 fps, 1979 Kbps, 01h28m02s
Audio : Dolby AC3, 48000 Hz, stereo, 192 kbps

DVDRip, English audio, no subtitles
